#    - plv8ify (divyenduz/plv8ify 161 stars — PLV8 JS-to-SQL;
#      FUTURE candidate)
#    - ts-sdks (MystenLabs/ts-sdks 96 stars — Sui TS SDKs codegen;
#      multi-component, FUTURE)
#    - aria-ui (ocavue/aria-ui 18 stars — Light-DOM web components;
